# Pre-push gate — typecheck + tests must pass before push. The
# pre-commit hook handles per-file lint+format+related-tests; this
# hook is the broader gate that catches "I forgot to run tests" or
# "the type system is unhappy somewhere I didn't touch."
#
# `pnpm doctor` composes typecheck + lint + test:fast --run. Tweak in
# package.json if the gate ever needs to broaden.
pnpm doctor
